Package com.commercetools.graphql.api.types

Class APIClientWithSecret

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.graphql.api.types.APIClientWithSecret
public class APIClientWithSecret extends Object
API Clients can be used to obtain OAuth 2 access tokens. The secret is only shown once in the response of creating the API Client.
